    <line>The name of the old man was De Lacey.</line>
    <line>He was decended from a good family in France <delSpan spanTo="#c57-0031.05" rend="strikethrough"/>&amp;</line>
    <line>untill very lately had lived<anchor xml:id="c57-0031.05"/> where for many years</line>
    <line> he had lived in affluence respected by his superiors</line>
    <line>&amp; beloved by his equals. <delSpan spanTo="#c57-0031.06" rend="strikethrough"/>His
      two children Felix &amp; Aga</line>
    <line>tha<anchor xml:id="c57-0031.06"/> His son was bred in the service of his country</line>
